data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! Stylish ranch-style home in quiet Gresham neighborhood! This home has been updated with a spacious open floor plan, wood floors, and a well-designed kitchen and island. Many new updates to enjoy, including a tiled shower with rainfall shower head, new composite roof, solar, bamboo floors in living room, and wired for electric car charging. Large, fenced yard has a firepit and endless swimming pool & hot tub combo, perfect for entertaining, relaxing, or enjoying a swim in your backyard!
